    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like whenever i read about this, people just call wind \"clean\" and gas \"dirty\" without looking at the actual numbers. do u think it's fair to call wind \"clean\" when there's so much habitat destruction and mining involved, or is that just a biased way of looking at it?",
